---
title: Moroccan Pork Tagine with Mint Couscous & Toasted Almonds
description: This Moroccan pork tagine gets its subtle sweetness from a secret ingredient - mango chutney! It adds a tasty boost and makes the sauce thick and rich. Served with a mint-infused couscous and topped with a nutty almond crunch, there are so many things to enjoy in this flavoursome bowl.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b63dd78ae08b523bb323007-04c990c8.jpg
